purpose: This file serves as the main entry point for a web application named 'Agentboostr - AI原生孵化器平台' (AI-native incubator platform). It sets up the basic HTML structure, metadata for SEO and social media sharing, and acts as a container for a client-side application.

key_content: Standard HTML5 document declaration and language setting.
Metadata in the <head> section including character set, viewport, title, description, and author information.
Open Graph (og:) and Twitter Card (twitter:) meta tags for rich social media previews, specifying title, description, type, and image.
A <body> section containing a <div id="root"> element, which is a common mount point for single-page applications (SPAs).
A <script> tag that imports '/src/main.tsx' as a module, indicating that the main application logic is written in TypeScript/TSX and will be dynamically loaded and rendered into the 'root' div.
metadata.summary: The `index.html` file is the foundational page for the Agentboostr web application. It provides essential HTML boilerplate, configures meta tags for search engine optimization and social media display, and crucially, includes a script that loads and executes the main TypeScript/TSX application, which will then render the user interface within the `<div id="root">`.
